      <h3>Welcome</h3>
      <p id="welcome-paragraph">I want to welcome everyone, and I would encourage you to post a short informal hello
        message in the "Introductions" discussion forum to let me know you
        received my welcome message, and to briefly introduce yourself to your fellow
        classmates.

      </p>


      <h3>Subjects</h3>
      <p id="sub-para">Here are the subjects that are been discussed in this website in details and also the neccesarry
        revision materials available</p>

      <div id="subject-list-all">

        <ul id="subject-list-1">
          <li class="subject">Mathematics</li>
          <li class="subject">English</li>
          <li class="subject">Kiswahili</li>
          <li class="subject">Chemistry</li>
          <li class="subject">Biology</li>
          <li class="subject">Agriculture</li>
        </ul>

